The evidence with the title 'Help fighting pay discrimination in Ohio would be a phone call ... ' says Mar 28, 2017  ... The average working woman in Ohio is paid only 75 percent of what her male counterpart gets paid , regardless of educational background and job description .  ... U.S. Census information shows by age 65 , the average woman will have lost $ 431,000 over her working lifetime as a result of the earnings gap. 
